  "texts": [
    "(37) is slightly different thanYeh et al. 's (2018) presentation.",
    "This alternate formulation requires specifying 2× larger.",
    "We selected this alternate presentation to provide consistency with later work (Tsai et al., 2023b; Chen et al., 2021)",
    "In practice, only a subset of { (0), …, (T-1) } is actually stored.",
    "Heuristics are then applied to this subset to achieve acceptable influence estimation error (Pruthi et al., 2020; Hammoudeh & Lowd, 2022)."
  ]
